</li>
<li sourcefile="PolishFunctionality/vat-reverse-charge-in-purchase-transactions.md" sourcestartlinenumber="133"><p sourcefile="PolishFunctionality/vat-reverse-charge-in-purchase-transactions.md" sourcestartlinenumber="133"><strong sourcefile="PolishFunctionality/vat-reverse-charge-in-purchase-transactions.md" sourcestartlinenumber="133">Data obowiązku VAT</strong> – data obowiązku VAT pobrana z parametrów
