</li>
<li sourcefile="PolishFunctionality/vat-reverse-charge-in-purchase-transactions.md" sourcestartlinenumber="137"><p sourcefile="PolishFunctionality/vat-reverse-charge-in-purchase-transactions.md" sourcestartlinenumber="137"><strong sourcefile="PolishFunctionality/vat-reverse-charge-in-purchase-transactions.md" sourcestartlinenumber="137">Kwota odwrotnego obciążenia</strong> – kwota obliczonego podatku VAT
